<p>Welcome to Wordzies, the interactive vocabulary building application.  Wordzies is all about repitition, which is the best way to learn and remember new words. We help you integrate your "wordzies" into your everyday vocabulary.  Sign in with your twitter account to start using wordzies now!</p>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span6">
    <div id='mywordzies'>
      <h1>Wordzies In Progress</h1>
	      <ul>
					<% if current_user %>
      		<% @words.each do |wordzy| %>
      		<li><%= link_to wordzy.wn_title, show_word_url(wordzy.wn_title) %></li>
      		<% end %>
      	</ul>
	<% else %>
	<li><%= link_to "Sign in to Add Words", "/auth/twitter" %></li>
	</ul>
		<% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

<div class="span5">
    <div id='randomwordzies'>
      <h1>Random Wordzies</h1>
	    <ul>
    		<% @suggested_words.each do |word| %>
    			<li><%= link_to word['word'], show_word_url(word['word']) %></li>
    		<% end %>
    	</ul>
			<%= link_to 'I already know these wordzies!', root_url %><br />
			<%= link_to 'I don\'t like these wordzies, suggest new ones!', root_url %>
	  </div>
  </div>
</div>

